{"authors":"杨宇虹","channel":"首页>煤矿安全监察>安全分析与事故通报","content":"<td class=\"font11pt lineHeight25\" id=\"artibody\"><font face=\"宋体\"> <p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 12pt; TEXT-INDENT: 21.1pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 19pt; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0; mso-line-height-rule: exactly\"><b style=\"mso-bidi-font-weight: normal\"><span style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-latin\">一、重大事故情况<span lang=\"EN-US\">\n      <o:p></o:p></span></span></b></p> <p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 12pt; TEXT-INDENT: 21pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 19pt; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0; mso-line-height-rule: exactly\"><span style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-latin\">发生重大事故<span lang=\"EN-US\"><font face=\"Calibri\">1</font><span style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-latin\">起、造成<span lang=\"EN-US\"><font face=\"Calibri\">20</font><span style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-latin\">人死亡。</span></span></span></span></span></p> <p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 12pt; TEXT-INDENT: 21pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 19pt; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0; mso-line-height-rule: exactly\"><span lang=\"EN-US\"><font face=\"Calibri\">3</font><span style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-latin\">月<span lang=\"EN-US\"><font face=\"Calibri\">23</font><span style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-latin\">日<span lang=\"EN-US\"><font face=\"Calibri\">23</font><span style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-latin\">时<span lang=\"EN-US\"><font face=\"Calibri\">46</font><span style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-latin\">分，山西朔州市山阴县，同煤集团同生公司安平矿爆破放顶后引起采空区大面积垮落，形成爆破冲击波，造成<span lang=\"EN-US\"><font face=\"Calibri\">20</font><span style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-latin\">人死亡、<span lang=\"EN-US\"><font face=\"Calibri\">1</font><span style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-latin\">人受伤。</span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></p> <p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 12pt; TEXT-INDENT: 21.1pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 19pt; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0; mso-line-height-rule: exactly\"><b style=\"mso-bidi-font-weight: normal\"><span style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-latin\">二、上周煤矿安全生产主要特点及警示<span lang=\"EN-US\">\n      <o:p></o:p></span></span></b></p> <p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 12pt; TEXT-INDENT: 21pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 19pt; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0; mso-line-height-rule: exactly\"><span style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-latin\">上周煤矿发生<span lang=\"EN-US\"><font face=\"Calibri\">1</font><span style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-latin\">起重大、<span lang=\"EN-US\"><font face=\"Calibri\">1</font><span style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-latin\">起较大事故，共造成<span lang=\"EN-US\"><font face=\"Calibri\">23</font><span style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-latin\">人死亡，事故起数、死亡人数环比均上升。暴露出煤矿企业安全生产主体责任落实不到位，隐患排查治理不彻底，复工复产检查环节不严格等问题。</span></span></span></span></span></span></span></p> <p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 12pt; TEXT-INDENT: 21pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 19pt; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0; mso-line-height-rule: exactly\"><span style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-latin\">防范措施：一是全面开展煤矿安全专项整治，强化安全监察执法，严把复产复工验收关；二是督促煤矿企业加强顶板管理，防止顶板大面积坍塌引发伤亡事故；三是矿井运输设备和钢丝绳要加强检修、检测，确保保护装置齐全、“一坡三挡”防护设施完善有效，坚决遏制煤矿重特大事故发生。</span></p> <p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 12pt; TEXT-INDENT: 21pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 19pt; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0; mso-line-height-rule: exactly\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">\n    <o:p>\n     <font face=\"Calibri\">&nbsp;</font>\n    </o:p></span></p></font></td>","createTime":1518425401952,"modules":[],"pubSource":"安全监管总局统计司","pubTime":1459094400000,"sourceName":"国家煤矿安全监察局","sourceType":1,"title":"2016年3月21日－3月27日煤矿安全生产简要情况","url":"http://www.chinacoal-safety.gov.cn/Contents/Channel_21857/2016/0329/266858/content_266858.htm"}
{"authors":"王超","channel":"首页>煤矿安全监察>各地安全","content":"<div class=\"display_nr pages_content\">\n <font face=\"宋体\"> <p style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 15.6pt; line-height: 28pt; text-indent: 32pt; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0; mso-line-height-rule: exactly;\"><span style=\"color: black; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 16pt; mso-ascii-font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;; mso-hansi-font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\">今年以来，福建煤监局始终把水害防治做为监察执法重点内容，加大水害防治检查力度，深入开展水害调查、分析和论证，进一步完善水害防治各项制度和措施，督促煤矿切实把水害防治各项工作部署落到实处。</span></p> <p style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 15.6pt; line-height: 28pt; text-indent: 32pt; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0; mso-line-height-rule: exactly;\"><span style=\"color: black; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 16pt; mso-ascii-font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;; mso-hansi-font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\">福建煤监局严格督促煤矿落实水害防治主体责任，在水害防治“八有”和“十个一律”基础上，建立“八个不准”和“五个严禁”等水害防治制度，并作为煤矿复工复产的必备条件以及日常监管监察的必查内容。同时制定《福建省煤矿水害防治工作方案》，要求煤矿每<span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"color: black; font-size: 16pt;\"><font face=\"Times New Roman\">3</font><span style=\"color: black; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 16pt; mso-ascii-font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;; mso-hansi-font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\">年必须委托有资质机构开展矿区水害调查，每年必须对矿井水文地质资料进行修订完善，煤矿水患调查分析报告必须经设区市煤炭行业管理部门组织技术论证。同时，还把水害防治作为煤矿建设项目安全设施“三同时”审查验收、颁发安全生产许可证的必备条件；作为安全生产标准化评级的必备条件。</span></span></span></p> <p style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 15.6pt; line-height: 28pt; text-indent: 32pt; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0; mso-line-height-rule: exactly;\"><span style=\"color: black; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 16pt; mso-ascii-font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;; mso-hansi-font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\">针对福建汛期特点，福建煤监局在汛期来临前，超前布置全省煤矿对矿井排水系统和所有工作面、井巷、地面边坡沟谷、煤台、矸石山、机房、车间、“两堂一舍”等重要场所和地点逐一排查整改，落实汛期应急所需的物资、设备和资金，做好专兼职救援队伍应急演练，并针对汛期特点开展煤矿水害防治专项监察。同时，福建各级煤矿安全监管部门建立与当地气象部门的沟通联系机制，及时收集并发布可能危及煤矿安全的暴雨洪水灾害信息。</span></p></font>\n</div>","createTime":1518425401964,"modules":[],"pubSource":"福建煤监局","pubTime":1514217600000,"region":["福建省"],"sourceName":"国家煤矿安全监察局","sourceType":1,"title":"福建煤监局强化煤矿水害治理","url":"http://www.chinacoal-safety.gov.cn/Contents/Channel_5517/2017/1226/300317/content_300317.htm"}
{"authors":"杨宇虹","channel":"首页>煤矿安全监察>要闻","content":"<div class=\"display_nr pages_content\">\n <font face=\"宋体\"> <p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 15.6pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 28pt; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-line-height-rule: exactly\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"FONT-SIZE: 16pt\">\n    <o:p>\n     <font face=\"Calibri\"> </font>\n    </o:p></span></p>\n  <table id=\"table1\" style=\"WIDTH: 731px; HEIGHT: 1052px\" height=\"1052\" cellspacing=\"4\" cellpadding=\"4\" width=\"731\" align=\"center\" border=\"0\"> \n   <tbody> \n    <tr> \n     <td> <p align=\"center\"><img src=\"http://www.chinacoal-safety.gov.cn/Contents/Channel_5474/2017/1213/299728/files_founder_1227430819/182614186.jpg\"></p> <p align=\"left\"><font face=\"宋体\"><font color=\"#0000ff\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"FONT-SIZE: 16pt; FONT-FAMILY: 楷体_GB2312; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-bidi-font-family: 'Times New Roman'; mso-bidi-theme-font: minor-bidi; mso-ansi-language: EN-US; mso-fareast-language: ZH-CN; mso-bidi-language: AR-SA\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 12<span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 16pt; FONT-FAMILY: 楷体_GB2312; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-bidi-font-family: 'Times New Roman'; mso-bidi-theme-font: minor-bidi; mso-ansi-language: EN-US; mso-fareast-language: ZH-CN; mso-bidi-language: AR-SA\">月<span lang=\"EN-US\">12日，第五届中俄安全生产高层对话在京举行。国家安全监管总局副局长、国家安全生产应急救援指挥中心主任孙华山出席对话活动。</span></span></span></font></font></p></td>\n    </tr> \n    <tr> \n     <td> <p align=\"center\"><img src=\"http://www.chinacoal-safety.gov.cn/Contents/Channel_5474/2017/1213/299728/files_founder_1227430819/1227024123.jpg\"></p> <p>　&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<font color=\"#0000ff\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"FONT-SIZE: 16pt; FONT-FAMILY: 楷体_GB2312; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-bidi-font-family: 'Times New Roman'; mso-bidi-theme-font: minor-bidi; mso-ansi-language: EN-US; mso-fareast-language: ZH-CN; mso-bidi-language: AR-SA\">12<span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 16pt; FONT-FAMILY: 楷体_GB2312; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-bidi-font-family: 'Times New Roman'; mso-bidi-theme-font: minor-bidi; mso-ansi-language: EN-US; mso-fareast-language: ZH-CN; mso-bidi-language: AR-SA\">月<span lang=\"EN-US\">12日，第五届中俄安全生产高层对话在京举行。国家安全监管总局副局长、国家煤矿安监局局长黄玉治出席对话活动。</span></span></span></font></p></td>\n    </tr>\n   </tbody>\n  </table><p></p> <p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 15.6pt; TEXT-INDENT: 32pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 28pt; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-line-height-rule: exactly; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"FONT-SIZE: 16pt\"><font face=\"Calibri\">12</font><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 16pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-fareast\">月<span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"FONT-SIZE: 16pt\"><font face=\"Calibri\">12</font><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 16pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-fareast\">日，第五届中俄安全生产高层对话在京举行。国家安全监管总局副局长、国家安全生产应急救援指挥中心主任孙华山<span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"FONT-SIZE: 16pt\"><font face=\"Calibri\">，</font><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 16pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-fareast\">总局副局长、国家煤矿安监局局长黄玉治，俄罗斯联邦环境、技术与原子能监察署副署长亚历山大•莱巴斯出席对话活动。<span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"FONT-SIZE: 16pt\">\n          <o:p></o:p></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></p> <p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 15.6pt; TEXT-INDENT: 32pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 28pt; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-line-height-rule: exactly; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\"><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 16pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-fareast\">孙华山首先向俄罗斯代表团的到来表示热烈欢迎。他指出，中国政府历来高度重视安全生产工作，党的十九大对安全生产提出了系列新的要求，为进一步做好安全生产工作指明了方向。他强调，当前中国“一带一路”战略与俄罗斯欧亚经济联盟加速对接，中俄原油管道工程等重要合作项目积极推进。保障两国重大合作工程和项目安全建设运行，促进经济社会健康有序发展，是双方的共同愿望和重大责任。中国国家安全监管总局愿与俄罗斯联邦环境、技术与原子能监察署一道，聚焦双方关注的议题与需要，以互利共赢为导向，共同办好中俄安全生产高层对话等合作平台，并在此基础上进一步扩大双边和多边框架下的交流，不断深化安全监管体制机制、科技创新、文化建设等方面的务实合作。<span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"FONT-SIZE: 16pt\">\n     <o:p></o:p></span></span></p> <p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 15.6pt; TEXT-INDENT: 32pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 28pt; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-line-height-rule: exactly; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\"><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 16pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-fareast\">莱巴斯在致辞中简要介绍了俄罗斯环境、技术与原子能监察署目前正在开展的风险导向型监管、远程监控技术和安全文化等重点工作。他指出，中俄安全生产高层对话对两国安全生产具有重要意义，是两国安全生产工作重要交流平台，希望进一步加强双方的交流与合作。他倡议建立煤矿安全监管机构论坛，邀请中国及各个产煤国监管机构参与，共同提升各国煤矿安全监管水平。<span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"FONT-SIZE: 16pt\">\n     <o:p></o:p></span></span></p> <p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 15.6pt; TEXT-INDENT: 32pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 28pt; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-line-height-rule: exactly; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\"><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 16pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-fareast\">黄玉治参加了下午的对话，在会议结束总结时强调，中俄两国都是世界主要新兴市场国家，都处在加快经济发展、改善人民生活的重要阶段，如何有效应对和解决发展过程中的安全生产问题，是双方共同面临的挑战。通过本次对话，不仅加深了中俄双方的相互了解与支持，增进了彼此友谊，而且加强了双方在安全生产领域的信息交流与共享，促进了共同发展。</span></p> <p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 15.6pt; TEXT-INDENT: 32pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 28pt; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-line-height-rule: exactly; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\" align=\"right\"><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 16pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-fareast\">（安全监管总局通信信息中心&nbsp; 田心/摄）</span></p></font>\n</div>","createTime":1518425401990,"modules":[],"pubSource":"安全监管总局国际合作司","pubTime":1513094400000,"sourceName":"国家煤矿安全监察局","sourceType":1,"title":"第五届中俄安全生产高层对话在京举行","url":"http://www.chinacoal-safety.gov.cn/Contents/Channel_5474/2017/1213/299728/content_299728.htm"}
{"authors":"李振营","channel":"首页>煤矿安全监察>重要通知","content":"<div class=\"display_nr pages_content\">\n <font face=\"宋体\"> <p style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: center; LINE-HEIGHT: 28pt; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 12pt; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-line-height-rule: exactly\" class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"center\"><b style=\"mso-bidi-font-weight: normal\"><span style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; FONT-SIZE: 20pt; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-fareast\">国家煤矿安监局办公室关于<span lang=\"EN-US\">\n      <!--?xml:namespace prefix = o ns = \r\n\"urn:schemas-microsoft-com:office:office\" /-->\n      <o:p></o:p></span></span></b></p> <p style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: center; LINE-HEIGHT: 28pt; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 12pt; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-line-height-rule: exactly\" class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"center\"><b style=\"mso-bidi-font-weight: normal\"><span style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; FONT-SIZE: 20pt; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-fareast\">开展煤矿井下作业人数情况调研的通知<span lang=\"EN-US\">\n      <o:p></o:p></span></span></b></p> <p style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: center; LINE-HEIGHT: 28pt; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 12pt; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-line-height-rule: exactly\" class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"center\"><span style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 楷体_GB2312; FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-hansi-font-family: 宋体\">煤安监司函办〔<span lang=\"EN-US\">2017〕<span lang=\"EN-US\">42号<span lang=\"EN-US\">\n       <o:p></o:p></span></span></span></span></p> <p style=\"LINE-HEIGHT: 28pt; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 12pt; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-line-height-rule: exactly\" class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-fareast\">各产煤省、自治区、直辖市及新疆生产建设兵团煤矿安全监管部门<span lang=\"EN-US\">:\n     <o:p></o:p></span></span></p> <p style=\"LINE-HEIGHT: 28pt; TEXT-INDENT: 32pt; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 12pt; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-line-height-rule: exactly; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\" class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-fareast\">为深入贯彻落实《关于减少井下作业人数提升煤矿安全保障能力的指导意见》（安监总煤行〔<span lang=\"EN-US\">2016〕<span lang=\"EN-US\">64号，以下简称《指导意见》）和《关于开展“机械化换人、自动化减人”科技强安专项行动的通知》（安监总科技〔<span lang=\"EN-US\">2015〕<span lang=\"EN-US\">63号）文件精神，了解煤矿井下作业人数现状及存在的问题，研究制定不同地区、不同生产能力、不同灾害类型、不同开采年限等条件下煤矿井下作业人数标准规范，定于<span lang=\"EN-US\">2017年<span lang=\"EN-US\">9~10月组织开展一次煤矿井下作业人数情况调研。现将有关事项通知如下：<span lang=\"EN-US\">\n           <o:p></o:p></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></p> <p style=\"LINE-HEIGHT: 28pt; TEXT-INDENT: 32pt; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 12pt; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-line-height-rule: exactly; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\" class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-fareast\">一、调研内容<span lang=\"EN-US\">\n     <o:p></o:p></span></span></p> <p style=\"LINE-HEIGHT: 28pt; TEXT-INDENT: 32pt; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 12pt; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-line-height-rule: exactly; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\" class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-fareast\">（一）《指导意见》等文件执行情况，包括优化生产组织，优化运输系统，优化井下劳动组织，推进机械化、自动化、信息化、智能化，推进巷道支护和修复技术创新及强化劳动定员管理等内容。<span lang=\"EN-US\">\n     <o:p></o:p></span></span></p> <p style=\"LINE-HEIGHT: 28pt; TEXT-INDENT: 32pt; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 12pt; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-line-height-rule: exactly; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\" class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-fareast\">（二）部分煤矿生产能力、投产时间、灾害类型、作业组织方式、入井人员数量、采区及工作面数量、采掘机械化程度、劳动定员标准制定及执行情况。<span lang=\"EN-US\">\n     <o:p></o:p></span></span></p> <p style=\"LINE-HEIGHT: 28pt; TEXT-INDENT: 32pt; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 12pt; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-line-height-rule: exactly; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\" class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-fareast\">（三）煤矿井下劳动定员存在的主要问题及建议。<span lang=\"EN-US\">\n     <o:p></o:p></span></span></p> <p style=\"LINE-HEIGHT: 28pt; TEXT-INDENT: 32pt; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 12pt; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-line-height-rule: exactly; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\" class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-fareast\">二、调研方式<span lang=\"EN-US\">\n     <o:p></o:p></span></span></p> <p style=\"LINE-HEIGHT: 28pt; TEXT-INDENT: 32pt; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 12pt; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-line-height-rule: exactly; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\" class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-fareast\">（一）问卷调查。在全国选取<span lang=\"EN-US\">957处生产煤矿作为调查样本，各省、区（市）根据样本分配数量表（见附件<span lang=\"EN-US\">1）组织填报《指导意见》文件落实情况表、煤矿井下作业人员情况调查表（见附件<span lang=\"EN-US\">2、附件<span lang=\"EN-US\">3）。样本选取要具有代表性，综合考虑井型、灾害类型和开采条件等因素。如辖区内有<span lang=\"EN-US\">2014年统计的原<span lang=\"EN-US\">47处“千人矿井”，需填报最新情况（名单见附件<span lang=\"EN-US\">4）。<span lang=\"EN-US\">\n            <o:p></o:p></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></p> <p style=\"LINE-HEIGHT: 28pt; TEXT-INDENT: 32pt; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 12pt; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-line-height-rule: exactly; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\" class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-fareast\">（二）实地调研。在问卷调查基础上，国家煤矿安监局行管司于<span lang=\"EN-US\">10月下旬组织有关人员赴部分省份进行现场调研，并对上报资料进行复核。<span lang=\"EN-US\">\n      <o:p></o:p></span></span></span></p> <p style=\"LINE-HEIGHT: 28pt; TEXT-INDENT: 32pt; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 12pt; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-line-height-rule: exactly; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\" class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-fareast\">三、有关要求<span lang=\"EN-US\">\n     <o:p></o:p></span></span></p> <p style=\"LINE-HEIGHT: 28pt; TEXT-INDENT: 32pt; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 12pt; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-line-height-rule: exactly; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\" class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-fareast\">请各单位认真组织调研工作，确保煤矿填报数据真实有效，并于<span lang=\"EN-US\">2017年<span lang=\"EN-US\">10月<span lang=\"EN-US\">20日前将调查表电子版报送国家安全监管总局研究中心。<span lang=\"EN-US\">\n        <o:p></o:p></span></span></span></span></span></p> <p style=\"LINE-HEIGHT: 28pt; TEXT-INDENT: 32pt; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 12pt; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-line-height-rule: exactly; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\" class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-fareast\">联系人及电话：程斌斌，<span lang=\"EN-US\">010-64463484（带传真）；<span lang=\"EN-US\">\n      <o:p></o:p></span></span></span></p> <p style=\"LINE-HEIGHT: 28pt; TEXT-INDENT: 32pt; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 12pt; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-line-height-rule: exactly; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\" class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-fareast\">电子邮箱：<span lang=\"EN-US\">fzzx5@vip.sina.com。<span lang=\"EN-US\">\n      <o:p></o:p></span></span></span></p> <p style=\"LINE-HEIGHT: 28pt; TEXT-INDENT: 32pt; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 12pt; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-line-height-rule: exactly; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\" class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-fareast\">附件：<span lang=\"EN-US\">1．<a href=\"http://www.chinasafety.gov.cn/newpage/newfiles/20170925fujian1.doc\" target=\"_blank\">样本分配数量表</a>&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span></p> <p style=\"LINE-HEIGHT: 28pt; TEXT-INDENT: 80pt; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 12pt; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-line-height-rule: exactly; mso-char-indent-count: 5.0\" class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-fareast\" lang=\"EN-US\">2.<span style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-fareast\"><a href=\"http://www.chinasafety.gov.cn/newpage/newfiles/20170925fujian2.doc\" target=\"_blank\"><span style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-fareast\">《指导意见》文件落实情况表</span></a>&nbsp;&nbsp; <span lang=\"EN-US\">\n      <o:p></o:p></span></span></span></p> <p style=\"LINE-HEIGHT: 28pt; TEXT-INDENT: 80pt; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 12pt; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-line-height-rule: exactly; mso-char-indent-count: 5.0\" class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-fareast\" lang=\"EN-US\">3<span style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-fareast\">．<span lang=\"EN-US\"><span style=\"mso-spacerun: yes\"><span style=\"TEXT-DECORATION: underline\"><a href=\"http://www.chinasafety.gov.cn/newpage/newfiles/20170925fujian3.doc\" target=\"_blank\"><span lang=\"EN-US\"><span style=\"mso-spacerun: yes\"><span style=\"TEXT-DECORATION: underline\">&nbsp; 省<span style=\"TEXT-DECORATION: underline\">&nbsp; 公司<span style=\"TEXT-DECORATION: underline\">&nbsp; 煤矿井下作业人员情况调查表</span></span></span></span></span></a>&nbsp; <span lang=\"EN-US\">\n         <o:p></o:p></span></span></span></span></span></span></p> <p style=\"LINE-HEIGHT: 28pt; TEXT-INDENT: 80pt; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 12pt; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-line-height-rule: exactly; mso-char-indent-count: 5.0\" class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-fareast\" lang=\"EN-US\">4<span style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-fareast\">．<a href=\"http://www.chinasafety.gov.cn/newpage/newfiles/20170925fujian4.doc\" target=\"_blank\"><span style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-fareast\">全国<span lang=\"EN-US\">47处单班入井超千人矿井名单（<span lang=\"EN-US\">2014年<span style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-fareast\">统计）</span></span></span></span></a><span style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-fareast\">&nbsp; <span lang=\"EN-US\">\n       <o:p></o:p></span></span></span></span></p> <p style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: right; LINE-HEIGHT: 28pt; TEXT-INDENT: 32pt; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 12pt; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-line-height-rule: exactly; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\" class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"right\"><span style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-fareast\">国家煤矿安监局办公室<span lang=\"EN-US\">\n     <o:p></o:p></span></span></p> <p style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: right; LINE-HEIGHT: 28pt; TEXT-INDENT: 32pt; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 12pt; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-line-height-rule: exactly; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\" class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"right\"><span style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-fareast\" lang=\"EN-US\">2017<span style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-fareast\">年<span lang=\"EN-US\">9月<span lang=\"EN-US\">20日<span lang=\"EN-US\">\n        <o:p></o:p></span></span></span></span></span></p></font>\n</div>","createTime":1518425402017,"modules":[],"pubSource":"煤矿安监局办公室","pubTime":1506268800000,"sourceName":"国家煤矿安全监察局","sourceType":1,"title":"国家煤矿安监局办公室关于","url":"http://www.chinacoal-safety.gov.cn/Con