class=\"MsoNormal\"> </p>\n   <table id=\"table1\" border=\"0\" cellspacing=\"6\" width=\"650\" align=\"center\"> \n    <tbody> \n     <tr> \n      <td><img src=\"http://www.chinacoal-safety.gov.cn/Contents/Channel_5474/2017/0907/294230/files_founder_2691728445/1161312706.jpg\"></td>\n     </tr> \n     <tr> \n      <td><span style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 楷体_GB2312; COLOR: blue; FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-hansi-font-family: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 1.0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: 'Times New Roman'; mso-ansi-language: EN-US; mso-fareast-language: ZH-CN; mso-bidi-language: AR-SA\" lang=\"EN-US\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 9<span style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 楷体_GB2312; COLOR: blue; FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-hansi-font-family: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 1.0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: 'Times New Roman'; mso-ansi-language: EN-US; mso-fareast-language: ZH-CN; mso-bidi-language: AR-SA\">月<span lang=\"EN-US\">7日<span style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 楷体_GB2312; COLOR: blue; FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-hansi-font-family: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 1.0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: 'Times New Roman'; mso-ansi-language: EN-US; mso-fareast-language: ZH-CN; mso-bidi-language: AR-SA\">，国家安全监管总局、国家煤矿安监局召开全国煤矿瓦斯防治工作视频会。<font face=\"宋体\"></font></span></span></span></span></td>\n     </tr>\n    </tbody>\n   </table><p></p></font> <p style=\"LINE-HEIGHT: 28pt; TEXT-INDENT: 32pt; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 15.6pt; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-line-height-rule: exactly; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\" class=\"MsoNormal\">\n   <st1:chsdate w:st=\"on\" isrocdate=\"False\" islunardate=\"False\" day=\"7\" month=\"9\" year=\"2017\">\n    <span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 16pt\" lang=\"EN-US\"><font face=\"Times New Roman\">9</font><span style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-ascii-font-family: 'Times New Roman'; mso-hansi-font-family: 'Times New Roman'\">月<span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 16pt\" lang=\"EN-US\"><font face=\"Times New Roman\">7</font><span style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-ascii-font-family: 'Times New Roman'; mso-hansi-font-family: 'Times New Roman'\">日<span style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-ascii-font-family: 'Times New Roman'; mso-hansi-font-family: 'Times New Roman'\">，国家安全监管总局、国家煤矿安监局召开全国煤矿瓦斯防治工作视频会，深入贯彻习近平总书记、李克强总理等中央领导同志关于安全生产工作重要讲话和指示批示精神，推动落实国务院安委会关于开展安全生产大检查的部署要求，总结交流煤矿瓦斯防治经验，研究安排下一步煤矿瓦斯防治重点工作，防范遏制煤矿重特大事故。国家安全监管总局副局长、国家煤矿安监局局长黄玉治出席会议并讲话，国家煤矿安监局副局长宋元明主持会议、副局长桂来保出席会议。<span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 16pt\" lang=\"EN-US\">\n          <o:p></o:p></span></span></span></span></span></span>\n   </st1:chsdate></p> <p style=\"LINE-HEIGHT: 28pt; TEXT-INDENT: 32pt; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 15.6pt; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-line-height-rule: exactly; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\" class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-ascii-font-family: 'Times New Roman'; mso-hansi-font-family: 'Times New Roman'\">黄玉治指出，近年来，全国煤矿瓦斯防治理念认识不断深化，政策支持力度不断加大，法规制度要求越来越严，管理水平不断提高，技术装备不断进步，执法效能不断提升，瓦斯防治工作取得了积极进展。但重特大瓦斯事故尚未有效遏制，在瓦斯防治思想认识、瓦斯地质资料、通风系统、瓦斯抽采、安全监控系统和保障能力等方面还存在诸多问题，煤矿瓦斯防治任务依然艰巨。<span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 16pt\" lang=\"EN-US\">\n     <o:p></o:p></span></span></p> <p style=\"LINE-HEIGHT: 28pt; TEXT-INDENT: 32pt; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 15.6pt; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-line-height-rule: exactly; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\" class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-ascii-font-family: 'Times New Roman'; mso-hansi-font-family: 'Times New Roman'\">黄玉治强调，各地区、有关部门和企业要进一步提升瓦斯防治工作摆位，强化“零超限”目标管理，以瓦斯地质和通风系统为基础，以区域治理为关键，以安全监控系统为保障，强化制度措施落实，推进综合治理，加大先进技术装备推广应用力度，强化瓦斯防治监管监察执法，不断提升煤矿瓦斯防治工作水平。同时，围绕瓦斯防治，要求各地加快淘汰退出不具备瓦斯防治能力的煤矿，做好保供应期间的煤矿安全生产工作，持续推进煤矿安全基础建设，以新的成绩迎接党的十九大胜利召开。<span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 16pt\" lang=\"EN-US\">\n     <o:p></o:p></span></span></p> <p style=\"LINE-HEIGHT: 28pt; TEXT-INDENT: 32pt; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 15.6pt; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-line-height-rule: exactly; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\" class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-ascii-font-family: 'Times New Roman'; mso-hansi-font-family: 'Times New Roman'\">会上，贵州省安监局（贵州煤监局）、陕西煤业化工集团和安徽淮北矿业集团等三家单位做了典型发言。</span></p><span style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-ascii-font-family: 'Times New Roman'; mso-hansi-font-family: 'Times New Roman'\"><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 16pt\" lang=\"EN-US\">\n    <o:p> \n     <p style=\"LINE-HEIGHT: 19pt; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 12pt; BACKGROUND: white; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-line-height-rule: exactly; mso-pagination: widow-orphan\" class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"right\" sizcache01880250819067248=\"3\" sizset=\"41\" sizcache07221656460821899=\"3\"><span style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; COLOR: #333333; FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri\">（安全监管总局通信信息中心<span style=\"COLOR: #333333; FONT-SIZE: 16pt\"><font face=\"Calibri\"> 田心</font><span style=\"COLOR: #333333; FONT-SIZE: 16pt\" lang=\"EN-US\"><font face=\"Calibri\">/</font><span style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; COLOR: #333333; FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri\">摄）<span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 16pt\" lang=\"EN-US\">\n           <o:p></o:p></span></span></span></span></span></p>\n    </o:p></span></span></font>\n</div>","createTime":1518425402425,"modules":[],"pubSource":"煤矿安监局办公室","pubTime":1504713600000,"sourceName":"国家煤矿安全监察局","sourceType":1,"title":"黄玉治在全国煤矿瓦斯防治工作视频会上强调：","url":"http://www.chinacoal-safety.gov.cn/Contents/Channel_5474/2017/0907/294230/content_294230.htm"}
{"authors":"李静","channel":"首页>煤矿安全监察>重要通知","content":"<div class=\"display_nr pages_content\">\n <font face=\"宋体\"> <p style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: center; LINE-HEIGHT: 28pt; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 12pt; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-line-height-rule: exactly\" class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"center\"><b style=\"mso-bidi-font-weight: normal\"><span style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; FONT-SIZE: 20pt; mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-latin\">国家煤矿安监局办公室关于召开</span></b><b style=\"mso-bidi-font-weight: normal\"><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 20pt\" lang=\"EN-US\">\n     <!--?xml:namespace prefix = o ns = \r\n\"urn:schemas-microsoft-com:office:office\" /-->\n     <o:p></o:p></span></b></p> <p style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: center; LINE-HEIGHT: 28pt; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 12pt; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-line-height-rule: exactly\" class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"center\"><b style=\"mso-bidi-font-weight: normal\"><span style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; FONT-SIZE: 20pt; mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-latin\">煤矿安全生产标准化矿井试点工作</span></b><b style=\"mso-bidi-font-weight: normal\"><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 20pt\" lang=\"EN-US\">\n     <o:p></o:p></span></b></p> <p style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: center; LINE-HEIGHT: 28pt; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 12pt; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-line-height-rule: exactly\" class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"center\"><b style=\"mso-bidi-font-weight: normal\"><span style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; FONT-SIZE: 20pt; mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-latin\">座谈会的通知</span></b><b style=\"mso-bidi-font-weight: normal\"><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 20pt\" lang=\"EN-US\">\n     <o:p></o:p></span></b></p> <p style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: center; LINE-HEIGHT: 28pt; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 12pt; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-line-height-rule: exactly\" class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"center\"><span style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 楷体_GB2312; FONT-SIZE: 16pt\">煤安监司函办〔<span lang=\"EN-US\">2017〕<span lang=\"EN-US\">5号<span lang=\"EN-US\">\n       <o:p></o:p></span></span></span></span></p> <p style=\"LINE-HEIGHT: 28pt; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 12pt; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-line-height-rule: exactly\" class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-latin\">各产煤省、自治区、直辖市及新疆生产建设兵团煤矿安全生产标准化工作主管部门：<span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 16pt\" lang=\"EN-US\">\n     <o:p></o:p></span></span></p> <p style=\"LINE-HEIGHT: 28pt; TEXT-INDENT: 32pt; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 12pt; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-line-height-rule: exactly; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\" class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-latin\">为推进各地按照新颁布的《煤矿安全生产标准化考核定级办法（试行）》和《煤矿安全生产标准化基本要求及评分方法（试行）》（煤安监行管〔<span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 16pt\" lang=\"EN-US\"><font face=\"Calibri\">2017</font><span style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-latin\">〕<span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 16pt\" lang=\"EN-US\"><font face=\"Calibri\">5</font><span style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-latin\">号，以下简称《新办法》）开展煤矿安全生产标准化矿井试点工作，定于<span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 16pt\" lang=\"EN-US\"><font face=\"Calibri\">2</font><span style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-latin\">月中旬在北京召开动员部署座谈会。现将有关事项通知如下：<span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 16pt\" lang=\"EN-US\">\n           <o:p></o:p></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></p> <p style=\"LINE-HEIGHT: 28pt; TEXT-INDENT: 32pt; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 12pt; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-line-height-rule: exactly; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\" class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-latin\">一、<span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 16pt\"><font face=\"Calibri\"> </font><span style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-latin\">会议内容<span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 16pt\" lang=\"EN-US\">\n       <o:p></o:p></span></span></span></span></p> <p style=\"LINE-HEIGHT: 28pt; TEXT-INDENT: 32pt; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 12pt; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-line-height-rule: exactly; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\" class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-latin\">（一）研究部署煤矿安全生产标准化矿井试点工作；<span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 16pt\" lang=\"EN-US\">\n     <o:p></o:p></span></span></p> <p style=\"LINE-HEIGHT: 28pt; TEXT-INDENT: 32pt; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 12pt; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-line-height-rule: exactly; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\" class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-latin\">（二）解读《新办法》。<span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 16pt\" lang=\"EN-US\">\n     <o:p></o:p></span></span></p> <p style=\"LINE-HEIGHT: 28pt; TEXT-INDENT: 32pt; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 12pt; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-line-height-rule: exactly; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\" class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-latin\">二、参会人员<span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 16pt\" lang=\"EN-US\">\n     <o:p></o:p></span></span></p> <p style=\"LINE-HEIGHT: 28pt; TEXT-INDENT: 32pt; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 12pt; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-line-height-rule: exactly; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\" class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-latin\">各产煤省（区、市）及新疆生产建设兵团煤矿安全生产标准化主管部门分管负责人或业务处室负责人<span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 16pt\" lang=\"EN-US\"><font face=\"Calibri\">1</font><span style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-latin\">人，业务人员<span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 16pt\" lang=\"EN-US\"><font face=\"Calibri\">1</font><span style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; 