{"authors":"田心","channel":"首页>煤矿安全监察>公告公文","content":"<td class=\"font14 lineHeight25\" id=\"artibody\"> <p style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: center; LINE-HEIGHT: 19pt; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 15.6pt; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-line-height-rule: exactly\" class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"center\"><b style=\"mso-bidi-font-weight: normal\"><span style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; FONT-SIZE: 20pt; mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri\">国家煤矿安监局办公室</span></b><b style=\"mso-bidi-font-weight: normal\"><span style=\"FONT-FAMILY: Calibri; FONT-SIZE: 20pt\" lang=\"EN-US\">\n    <!--?xml:namespace prefix \r\n= o ns = \"urn:schemas-microsoft-com:office:office\" /-->\n    <o:p></o:p></span></b></p> <p style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: center; LINE-HEIGHT: 19pt; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 15.6pt; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-line-height-rule: exactly\" class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"center\"><b style=\"mso-bidi-font-weight: normal\"><span style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; FONT-SIZE: 20pt; mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri\">关于报送煤矿建设项目“三同时”和</span></b><b style=\"mso-bidi-font-weight: normal\"><span style=\"FONT-FAMILY: Calibri; FONT-SIZE: 20pt\" lang=\"EN-US\">\n    <o:p></o:p></span></b></p> <p style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: center; LINE-HEIGHT: 19pt; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 15.6pt; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-line-height-rule: exactly\" class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"center\"><b style=\"mso-bidi-font-weight: normal\"><span style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; FONT-SIZE: 20pt; mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri\">安全生产许可证管理工作总结的函</span></b><b style=\"mso-bidi-font-weight: normal\"><span style=\"FONT-FAMILY: Calibri; FONT-SIZE: 20pt\" lang=\"EN-US\">\n    <o:p></o:p></span></b></p> <p style=\"LINE-HEIGHT: 28pt; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 15.6pt; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-line-height-rule: exactly\" class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-ascii-font-family: 'Times New Roman'; mso-hansi-font-family: 'Times New Roman'\">各省级煤矿安全监察局：<span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 16pt\" lang=\"EN-US\">\n    <o:p></o:p></span></span></p> <p style=\"LINE-HEIGHT: 28pt; TEXT-INDENT: 32pt; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 15.6pt; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-line-height-rule: exactly; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\" class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-ascii-font-family: 'Times New Roman'; mso-hansi-font-family: 'Times New Roman'\">现就报送<span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 16pt\" lang=\"EN-US\">2017<span style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-ascii-font-family: 'Times New Roman'; mso-hansi-font-family: 'Times New Roman'\">年煤矿建设项目“三同时”、安全生产许可证颁发管理工作总结材料有关事项通知如下：<span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 16pt\" lang=\"EN-US\">\n      <o:p></o:p></span></span></span></span></p> <p style=\"LINE-HEIGHT: 28pt; TEXT-INDENT: 32pt; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 15.6pt; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-line-height-rule: exactly; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\" class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-ascii-font-family: 'Times New Roman'; mso-hansi-font-family: 'Times New Roman'\">一、报送内容<span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 16pt\" lang=\"EN-US\">\n    <o:p></o:p></span></span></p> <p style=\"LINE-HEIGHT: 28pt; TEXT-INDENT: 32pt; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 15.6pt; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-line-height-rule: exactly; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\" class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-ascii-font-family: 'Times New Roman'; mso-hansi-font-family: 'Times New Roman'\">（一）<span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 16pt\" lang=\"EN-US\">2017<span style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-ascii-font-family: 'Times New Roman'; mso-hansi-font-family: 'Times New Roman'\">年煤矿建设项目“三同时”工作情况。对煤矿建设项目安全核准、安全设施设计审查、安全设施竣工验收监督核查工作及相关工作制度建立等情况进行总结并填写附表（见附件<span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 16pt\" lang=\"EN-US\">1<span style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-ascii-font-family: 'Times New Roman'; mso-hansi-font-family: 'Times New Roman'\">、<span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 16pt\" lang=\"EN-US\">2<span style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-ascii-font-family: 'Times New Roman'; mso-hansi-font-family: 'Times New Roman'\">、<span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 16pt\" lang=\"EN-US\">3<span style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-ascii-font-family: 'Times New Roman'; mso-hansi-font-family: 'Times New Roman'\">），提炼工作中好的做法和经验，分析存在的主要问题，提出加强和改进煤矿建设项目监察工作的意见建议<span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 16pt\" lang=\"EN-US\">,<span style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-ascii-font-family: 'Times New Roman'; mso-hansi-font-family: 'Times New Roman'\">以及下一步安全生产许可事项移交后，加强煤矿建设项目“三同时”事前、事中、事后监察工作的思路和建议。<span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 16pt\" lang=\"EN-US\">\n              <o:p></o:p></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></p> <p style=\"LINE-HEIGHT: 28pt; TEXT-INDENT: 32pt; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 15.6pt; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-line-height-rule: exactly; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\" class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-ascii-font-family: 'Times New Roman'; mso-hansi-font-family: 'Times New Roman'\">（二）<span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 16pt\" lang=\"EN-US\">2017<span style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-ascii-font-family: 'Times New Roman'; mso-hansi-font-family: 'Times New Roman'\">年煤矿安全生产许可证颁发和管理工作情况。对安全生产许可证颁发管理工作进行总结并填写附表（见附件<span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 16pt\" lang=\"EN-US\">4<span style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-ascii-font-family: 'Times New Roman'; mso-hansi-font-family: 'Times New Roman'\">、<span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 16pt\" lang=\"EN-US\">5<span style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-ascii-font-family: 'Times New Roman'; mso-hansi-font-family: 'Times New Roman'\">），提炼健全完善安全许可工作制度、严格安全许可标准和程序、严格颁证条件审查和现场核查、组织开展专项监察、加强安全许可基础工作等方面的经验和做法；分析存在的主要问题和不足，包括面临的困难和排查安全生产许可证有效期满但未依法注销情况；需要进一步改进和提高的方面；下一步安全生产许可事项移交地方后，加强煤矿安全生产许可事前、事中、事后监察工作的思路和建议。<span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 16pt\" lang=\"EN-US\">\n          <o:p></o:p></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></p> <p style=\"LINE-HEIGHT: 28pt; TEXT-INDENT: 32pt; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 15.6pt; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-line-height-rule: exactly; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\" class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-ascii-font-family: 'Times New Roman'; mso-hansi-font-family: 'Times New Roman'\">二、有关要求<span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 16pt\" lang=\"EN-US\">\n    <o:p></o:p></span></span></p> <p style=\"LINE-HEIGHT: 28pt; TEXT-INDENT: 32pt; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 15.6pt; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-line-height-rule: exactly; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\" class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-ascii-font-family: 'Times New Roman'; mso-hansi-font-family: 'Times New Roman'\">（一）请督促并指导企业务必于<span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 16pt\" lang=\"EN-US\">12<span style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-ascii-font-family: 'Times New Roman'; mso-hansi-font-family: 'Times New Roman'\">月底前更新煤矿安全生产基础管理数据平台中煤矿安全生产许可证、煤矿建设项目有关信息，使数据平台信息与实际保持一致。国家煤矿安监局将于明年<span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 16pt\" lang=\"EN-US\">1<span style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-ascii-font-family: 'Times New Roman'; mso-hansi-font-family: 'Times New Roman'\">月份对各省基础数据填报情况进行通报。<span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 16pt\" lang=\"EN-US\">\n        <o:p></o:p></span></span></span></span></span></span></p> <p style=\"LINE-HEIGHT: 28pt; TEXT-INDENT: 32pt; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 15.6pt; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-line-height-rule: exactly; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\" class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-ascii-font-family: 'Times New Roman'; mso-hansi-font-family: 'Times New Roman'\">（二）请于\n   <!--?xml:namespace \r\nprefix = st1 ns = \"urn:schemas-microsoft-com:office:smarttags\" /-->\n   <st1:chsdate w:st=\"on\" isrocdate=\"False\" islunardate=\"False\" day=\"20\" month=\"12\" year=\"2017\">\n    <span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 16pt\" lang=\"EN-US\">12<span style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-ascii-font-family: 'Times New Roman'; mso-hansi-font-family: 'Times New Roman'\">月<span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 16pt\" lang=\"EN-US\">20<span style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; FONT-SIZE: 1