ast-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-latin\">各产煤省、自治区、直辖市及新疆生产建设兵团煤矿安全培训主管部门：<span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 16pt\" lang=\"EN-US\">\n     <o:p></o:p></span></span></p> <p style=\"LINE-HEIGHT: 28pt; TEXT-INDENT: 32pt; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 12pt; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-line-height-rule: exactly; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\" class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-latin\">现将汇编形成的《<a href=\"http://www.chinasafety.gov.cn/newpage/newfiles/20170707mt.pdf\" target=\"_blank\">煤矿企业安全培训违法违规行为处罚情形一览表</a>》予以印发，便于你们在煤矿安全培训监督检查执法中执行。</span></p> <p style=\"LINE-HEIGHT: 28pt; TEXT-INDENT: 32pt; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 12pt; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-line-height-rule: exactly; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\" class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-latin\">附件：<a href=\"http://www.chinasafety.gov.cn/newpage/newfiles/20170707mt.pdf\" target=\"_blank\">煤矿企业安全培训违法违规行为处罚情形一览表</a></span></p> <p style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: right; LINE-HEIGHT: 28pt; TEXT-INDENT: 32pt; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 12pt; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-line-height-rule: exactly; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\" class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"right\"><span style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-latin\">国家煤矿安监局办公室<span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 16pt\" lang=\"EN-US\">\n     <o:p></o:p></span></span></p> <p style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: right; LINE-HEIGHT: 28pt; TEXT-INDENT: 32pt; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 12pt; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-line-height-rule: exactly; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\" class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"right\"><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 16pt\" lang=\"EN-US\"><font face=\"Calibri\">2017</font><span style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-latin\">年<span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 16pt\" lang=\"EN-US\"><font face=\"Calibri\">6</font><span style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-latin\">月<span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 16pt\" lang=\"EN-US\"><font face=\"Calibri\">29</font><span style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-latin\">日<span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 16pt\" lang=\"EN-US\">\n          <o:p></o:p></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></p></font>\n</div>","createTime":1518425403895,"modules":[],"pubSource":"煤矿安监局办公室","pubTime":1499356800000,"sourceName":"国家煤矿安全监察局","sourceType":1,"title":"国家煤矿安监局办公室关于印发《煤矿企业","url":"http://www.chinacoal-safety.gov.cn/Contents/Channel_5476/2017/0707/290946/content_290946.htm"}
{"authors":"杨宇虹","channel":"首页>煤矿安全监察>安全分析与事故通报","content":"<td class=\"font11pt lineHeight25\" id=\"artibody\"><font face=\"宋体\"> <p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 12pt; TEXT-INDENT: 21pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 19pt; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0; mso-line-height-rule: exactly\"><span style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-latin\"><strong>一、重大事故情况</strong></span></p> <p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 12pt; TEXT-INDENT: 21pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 19pt; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0; mso-line-height-rule: exactly\"><span style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-latin\">发生重大事故<span lang=\"EN-US\"><font face=\"Calibri\">1</font><span style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-latin\">起、造成<span lang=\"EN-US\"><font face=\"Calibri\">10</font><span style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-latin\">人死亡和被困。</span></span></span></span></span></p> <p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 12pt; TEXT-INDENT: 21pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 19pt; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0; mso-line-height-rule: exactly\"><span lang=\"EN-US\"><font face=\"Calibri\">4</font><span style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-latin\">月<span lang=\"EN-US\"><font face=\"Calibri\">3</font><span style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-latin\">日<span lang=\"EN-US\"><font face=\"Calibri\">18</font><span style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-latin\">时<span lang=\"EN-US\"><font face=\"Calibri\">35</font><span style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-latin\">分，新疆喀什地区莎车县，天利煤矿发生顶板事故，造成<span lang=\"EN-US\"><font face=\"Calibri\">5</font><span style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-latin\">人死亡、<span lang=\"EN-US\"><font face=\"Calibri\">5</font><span style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-latin\">人被困、<span lang=\"EN-US\"><font face=\"Calibri\">1</font><span style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-latin\">人受伤。</span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></p> <p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 12pt; TEXT-INDENT: 21pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 19pt; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0; mso-line-height-rule: exactly\"><span style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-latin\"><strong>二、上周煤矿安全生产主要特点及警示</strong></span></p> <p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 12pt; TEXT-INDENT: 21pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 19pt; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0; mso-line-height-rule: exactly\"><span style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-latin\">上周煤矿发生重大事故，造成<span lang=\"EN-US\"><font face=\"Calibri\">10</font><span style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-latin\">人死亡，该煤矿企业安全生产许可证过期违规组织生产，暴露出企业法制意识淡薄、安全生产主体责任不落实，隐患排查治理不彻底，现场管理混乱等问题。</span></span></span></p> <p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 12pt; TEXT-INDENT: 21pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 19pt; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0; mso-line-height-rule: exactly\"><span style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-latin\">防范措施：一是要督促煤矿企业进一步落实安全生产主体责任，严格落实安全生产许可证制度，杜绝无照或证照过期生产经营。二是全面开展煤矿安全专项整治，全面排查治理安全生产隐患，特别是要加强顶板管理，防止顶板大面积坍塌引发伤亡事故。</span></p> <p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 12pt; TEXT-INDENT: 21pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 19pt; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0; mso-line-height-rule: exactly\"><span lang=\"EN-US\"><span style=\"mso-spacerun: yes\">&nbsp;</span></span></p></font></td>","createTime":1518425403915,"modules":[],"pubSource":"安全监管总局统计司","pubTime":1459785600000,"sourceName":"国家煤矿安全监察局","sourceType":1,"title":"2016年3月28日－4月4日煤矿安全生产简要情况","url":"http://www.chinacoal-safety.gov.cn/Contents/Channel_21857/2016/0405/267616/content_267616.htm"}
{"authors":"李振营","channel":"首页>煤矿安全监察>公告公文","content":"<div class=\"display_nr pages_content\">\n <font face=\"宋体\"> <p style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: center; LINE-HEIGHT: 28pt; TEXT-INDENT: 40.15pt; MARGIN: 12pt 0cm 0pt; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0; mso-line-height-rule: exactly\" class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"center\"><b style=\"mso-bidi-font-weight: normal\"><span style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; FONT-SIZE: 20pt; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-fareast\">国家煤矿安监局关于对拟命名<span lang=\"EN-US\">2017年<span lang=\"EN-US\">\n       <o:p></o:p></span></span></span></b></p> <p style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: center; LINE-HEIGHT: 28pt; TEXT-INDENT: 40.15pt; MARGIN: 12pt 0cm 0pt; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0; mso-line-height-rule: exactly\" class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"center\"><b style=\"mso-bidi-font-weight: normal\"><span style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; FONT-SIZE: 20pt; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-fareast\">第一批一级安全生产标准化</span></b><b style=\"mso-bidi-font-weight: normal\"><span style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; FONT-SIZE: 20pt; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-fareast\">煤矿的公示<span lang=\"EN-US\">\n      <o:p></o:p></span></span></b></p> <p style=\"LINE-HEIGHT: 28pt; TEXT-INDENT: 32pt; MARGIN: 12pt 0cm 0pt; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0; mso-line-height-rule: exactly\" class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-fareast\">按照国家煤矿安监局印发的《煤矿安全生产标准化考核定级办法（试行）》和《煤矿安全生产标准化基本要求及评分方法（试行）》（煤安监行管﹝<span lang=\"EN-US\">2017﹞<span lang=\"EN-US\">5号）的有关规定，现已完成<span lang=\"EN-US\">8个省（区、市）申报的<span lang=\"EN-US\">80处一级安全生产标准化煤矿的资料审查和现场检查考核工作。有<span lang=\"EN-US\">62处煤矿达到一级安全生产标准化标准，现予以公示，接受社会监督。<span lang=\"EN-US\">\n          <o:p></o:p></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></p> <p style=\"LINE-HEIGHT: 28pt; TEXT-INDENT: 32pt; MARGIN: 12pt 0cm 0pt; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0; mso-line-height-rule: exactly\" class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-fareast\">公示期间，如发现申报煤矿存在瞒报事故、弄虚作假等违法违规行为的，将依规定取消其申报资格。<span lang=\"EN-US\">\n     <o:p></o:p></span></span></p> <p style=\"LINE-HEIGHT: 28pt; TEXT-INDENT: 32pt; MARGIN: 12pt 0cm 0pt; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0; mso-line-height-rule: exactly\" class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-fareast\">对公示煤矿有异议的，请于公示之日起<span lang=\"EN-US\">7日内将有关书面材料寄（或传真）到国家煤矿安监局行管司。单位反映情况要加盖公章，个人反映情况要用真实姓名并提供联系方式，以方便核实。<span lang=\"EN-US\">\n      <o:p></o:p></span></span></span></p> <p style=\"LINE-HEIGHT: 28pt; TEXT-INDENT: 32pt; MARGIN: 12pt 0cm 0pt; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0; mso-line-height-rule: exactly\" class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-fareast\">联系人：梁子荣、刘波；<span lang=\"EN-US\">\n     <o:p></o:p></span></span></p> <p style=\"LINE-HEIGHT: 28pt; TEXT-INDENT: 32pt; MARGIN: 12pt 0cm 0pt; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0; mso-line-height-rule: exactly\" class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-fareast\">联系电话：<span lang=\"EN-US\">010-64464789、<span lang=\"EN-US\">64464294（带传真）；<span lang=\"EN-US\">\n       <o:p></o:p></span></span></span></span></p> <p style=\"LINE-HEIGHT: 28pt; TEXT-INDENT: 32pt; MARGIN: 12pt 0cm 0pt; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0; mso-line-height-rule: exactly\" class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-fareast\">地址：北京市东城区和平里北街<span lang=\"EN-US\">21号；<span lang=\"EN-US\">\n      <o:p></o:p></span></span></span></p> <p style=\"LINE-HEIGHT: 28pt; TEXT-INDENT: 32pt; MARGIN: 12pt 0cm 0pt; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0; mso-line-height-rule: exactly\" class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-fareast\">邮编：<span lang=\"EN-US\">100713。<span lang=\"EN-US\">\n      <o:p></o:p></span></span></span></p> <p style=\"LINE-HEIGHT: 28pt; TEXT-INDENT: 32pt; MARGIN: 12pt 0cm 0pt; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0; mso-line-height-rule: exactly\" class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-fareast\">附件：<a href=\"http://www.chinasafety.gov.cn/newpage/newfiles/20171018fujian.doc\" target=\"_blank\">拟命名的<span lang=\"EN-US\">2017年第一批一级安全生产标准化煤矿名单</span></a>&nbsp; <span lang=\"EN-US\">\n     <o:p></o:p></span></span></p> <p style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: right; LINE-HEIGHT: 28pt; TEXT-INDENT: 32pt; MARGIN: 12pt 0cm 0pt; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0; mso-line-height-rule: exactly\" class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"right\"><span style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-fareast\" lang=\"EN-US\">2017<span style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-fareast\">年<span lang=\"EN-US\">10月<span lang=\"EN-US\">18日<span lang=\"EN-US\">\n        <o:p></o:p></span></span></span></span></span></p></font>\n</div>","createTime":1518425403936,"modules":[],"pubSource":"煤矿安监局行业安全基础管理指导司","pubTime":1508256000000,"sourceName":"国家煤矿安全监察局","sourceType":1,"title":"国家煤矿安监局关于对拟命名","url":"http://www.chinacoal-safety.gov.cn/Contents/Channel_5475/2017/1018/296767/content_296767.htm"}
